<div class="home-hero col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">
	<div class="home-hero-content">
		<h1>#GONOW</h1>
		<h4>It might be now or never</h4>
		<%= button_to 'Find Jobs Abroad', jobs_path, class: :"btn btn-warning", method: :get %>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="home-checklist">
	<div class="home-checklist-content col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
		<h3><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o"></i> Awesome Perks</h3>
		<p>Many jobs offer free housing, free airfare, medical insurance, and of course, paid vacation days! Take advantage of great perks.
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="home-checklist-content col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
		<h3><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o"></i>  New Experiences</h3>
		<p>It's a great big world out there. Discover new cultures, explore new sights, taste new foods. Travel and travel some more!</p>
	</div>
	<div class="home-checklist-content col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
		<h3><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o"></i> Travel Around</h3>
		<p>Take the weekends off to travel to new cities or countries with your new friends. New destinations are so close by.</p>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="home-newsletter col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">
	<div class="home-newsletter-content">
		<h4>Get a weekly email of the best new jobs abroad</h4>
